Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:29.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從那以後已經過了好長時間 哮喘也已經全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:33.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對空氣敏感的特點卻一直沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:01.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}

Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:01.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:18.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早安 誒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:23.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 看起來心事很重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:28.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們到底是是不被歡迎呢 氣氛好沉重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:33.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天居然被那麼正式地否定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:25.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\blur5\pos(1095,580)}{\pos(980,560)}{\3c&HB58E00&}{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs40\fad(500,300)}拒絕色的烹飪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:38.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個氛圍的中心 就是她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:42.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}成績優秀 認真 有威信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:46.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正是結女的代表呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:49.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且聽說還是學園理事長的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:55.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣的人物拒絕合併的話 對結女的其他人也會產生影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:01.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至少我是不歡迎你們男生的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為這個結姬女子學園是女校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:12.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是說 能夠改變這樣氣氛的關鍵也是她了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:23.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早安 瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:45.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想要能溝通的話 還是需要些時間的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:51.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你看起來一副忐忑不安的樣子呢 新吾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔在教室也是女僕裝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:04:01.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 安潔從母親那代開始就是女僕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:04.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}順便說一句 母親是英國人 所以我是混血兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:13.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學園長承認的野生女僕是同班同學的事雖然還沒能適應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:18.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是… 最重要的還是她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時的邂逅就像夢境一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:45.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:46.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:51.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}糟糕 我到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒注意 真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:02.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生請使用男生臨時洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 接下來是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:21.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:37.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本來就是少女的花園 所以沒料到會有男生在這裡學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生更衣室也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:44.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在庭院的偏僻處換衣服可是很痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:51.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正是這種時候 作為學生會會長的你更應該做點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:57.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你這麼說 我還有各務台的工作要做 很忙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}兩個人好像都沒有能放鬆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:02.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:04.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}應該說 為什麼是體操服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:05.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:09.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很遺憾沒有女僕用的體操服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:12.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是安潔一直都是女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:16.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以給大家帶來了慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:21.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽說燒水壺的水 無論大家有多麼勞累也能馬上變得有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:24.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像在什麼地方有些誤解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 謝謝你帶來的水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔不反對合併學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:40.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 安潔即使學生數增多了 也不在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:46.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能夠成為安潔主人的人 或許能夠增加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:51.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結女的女生 要是都像安潔那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:54.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用那麼在意也無所謂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是乾 紗凪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:02.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然反對的人也有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:08.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但也去接受了 這就是所謂的溫柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:11.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 小紗真的是好溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔好感動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:15.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不… 不是那麼回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:20.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等我 小紗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:25.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不是所有人都反對合併學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:32.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是只要她還在反對 氣氛就不會改善吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:46.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了 總之就努力打開她的心結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:48.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:58.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 你可真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:01.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的 這是誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:02.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}敲門一下是會怎樣阿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:13.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 真的是很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:19.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經沒關係了 我已經知道瓜生是那樣的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}粉 粉筆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:52.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}偷窺 聽說瓜生是首犯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:55.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了偷窺瀨名的裙子下面 故意將粉筆給…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:58.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}連我們學校的女生都成為敵人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}氣氛變得更糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:04.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但這可真不像新吾一貫的作風呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:09:00.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被發現後 還在狡辯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:16.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉 好像教室裏越來越沒有容身之處了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:23.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喔 今天也努力做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起了 櫻乃

Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:29.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}叫我的嗎

Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:35.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 好像在哪裡看過一樣

Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:42.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我是瓜生 要吃便當嗎

Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:45.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小熊喵 在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 小熊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:09.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:14.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫天羽美羽 是三年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 三年級生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:23.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫瓜生新吾 二年級生 那個各務台的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:26.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}試驗班的吧 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:34.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 你好 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:36.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:40.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我從小學開始就一直是在女校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和男生說話對我很新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:48.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真好啊 一二年級有試驗生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:58.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 想到前輩歡迎我們 就很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起來很好吃的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:07.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 妹妹想著 到了一個新學校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:11.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}於是努力做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 好孩子 好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:23.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然在適應前會很辛苦 但這是個很好的學園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:27.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生一定也會喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 今後也多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:45.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}天羽美羽前輩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我這裡是這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:54.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還算是歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 可能因為我也是女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這或許也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:08.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是沒關係 哥哥一直很擅長對付女性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:11.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說得我好像花花公子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:17.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這個意思 哥哥和我在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:24.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要保持哥哥平時的樣子就可以了 我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:29.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:39.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和各務台的同學們一起度過的這段時間 什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:42.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生比想象中的還要下流
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:45.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有女生在的時候輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}應該將他們給趕出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說話也很粗魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做事都很小孩子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:56.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}評價很差啊 男生們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:13:01.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是試驗生來了之後 開始注重儀容的女生沒有增加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:02.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實是有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:03.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}儀容是開始注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:08.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有意識到異性的存在 這樣的地方就容易粗心大意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:10.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}既然作為女人生出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:14.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就該磨礪自己 成為一個好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:18.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天開始 特別課程也重新進行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生 加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:24.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女生 也不要被看到弱點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就是特別課程嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:36.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不錯 不僅僅是料理 還有裁縫 茶道 花道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:39.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣必備的素質全部都有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:42.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了磨練女性的能力的特別課程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:47.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:49.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們也要磨練女性的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:56.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天一起做栗子飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:59.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}T組已經分好小組了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:03.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}6個人分成一個小組
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:08.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結女 各務台女生 男生分別兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:09.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一下子就是和女生一起的實習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:13.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果做得不好 肯定會更加被反感了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:22.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要保持哥哥平時的樣子就可以了 我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:27.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想瓜生一定也會喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:34.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之 儘量能夠不拖別人後腿 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:40.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你妨礙我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:48.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剝慄子的皮真難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:51.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說交給你就可以的 是椋梨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:56.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剝慄子皮的時候 請注意菜刀的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:04.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 真熟練的手法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:05.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乾 這裡準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:12.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 順利剝開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 謝謝你教我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:18.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}米還沒洗呢 我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾經常做料理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是幫忙打下手的程度而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:40.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生也不會去妨礙人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:43.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且剝皮的手法也很高超
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 只要模仿新吾就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:55.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣的程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:57.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:01.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不錯 不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生們也開始能幫上忙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然沒有瓜生那樣的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:11.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不會輸的 新吾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}堵上女僕的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:16.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔更能幫上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:25.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來只要等煮熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:31.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}男生和女生互相幫忙 這是一個不錯的機會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:32.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:46.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名 需要我幫什麼忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不需要 請不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪 把剩下的牛蒡材料給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是一點不浪費啊 愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:00.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 我們的小組連味繒湯都做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:04.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名不僅學習好 料理也很有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:09.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要先把殘渣除去 剩下的就簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:12.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是那步驟卻很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:16.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那只能去適應了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:21.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名是那種就算沒有異性的眼光 也不會有疏漏的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做得可真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:37.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}畢竟 食材可以隨便使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:41.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說需要 安潔就一直拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:43.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可沒那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:48.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們明白的吧 特別課程做的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:51.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有全部吃掉的話 是不給成績的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:04.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我肚子餓極了 給我上最大碗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:07.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是 拜託給我最大碗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:10.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我開動了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再來一碗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:30.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:53.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很能幹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:03.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多謝款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:19.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那明天再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:21.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:25.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 今天稍微有精神點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:29.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:39.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個是…

Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:46.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是謎之生物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:48.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 是她的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:49.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:55.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 見過一面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:59.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不久前見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:11.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}試驗合校 已經過了一周了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:12.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:16.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}選舉班長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:17.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果能快點選舉出班長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:21.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}老師 老師會很感激的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:22.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為是一個班級
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:30.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以從結女和各務台各選出一名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我pass
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:39.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}應該說 沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:43.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且我還擔任著各務台的學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:47.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在這裡的學生會 也有著副會長的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}於是 我推薦新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:54.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:55.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:20:59.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:04.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾的話 能夠看清楚氣氛 把事情做好的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:07.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:15.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}知道了  那我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:17.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會忙起來的

Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:27.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後 被選舉出來的人站起來 向大家問好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:30.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:31.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:36.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 果然是新吾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 能夠接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:41.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那邊也是理所當然的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:48.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那確實是 那樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這不是開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:53.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼會和那樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}

